# ── Twilio (for auto SMS/WhatsApp reminders) ─────────────────────────────
# These are NOT browser env vars — set them as Edge Function secrets in:
# Supabase Dashboard → Project → Edge Functions → Manage secrets
#
#   TWILIO_ACCOUNT_SID      (from console.twilio.com)
#   TWILIO_AUTH_TOKEN       (from console.twilio.com)
#   TWILIO_FROM_SMS         e.g. +14155552671  (your Twilio number)
#   TWILIO_FROM_WHATSAPP    e.g. whatsapp:+14155238886  (Twilio sandbox default)
#
# Deploy the edge function with:
#   npx supabase functions deploy send-reminder
